-10-17T06:51:31.000Z","msg":"721有充分證據證明警察失職先啦<br />\n<br />\n1. 999 接報後無安排人手、cut線甚至offline<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 兩名警員配合白衫暴徒行動，巡邏至恐襲現場自動轉身離開。<br />\n<br />\n3. 警隊遲到39分鐘到場前白衫暴徒自行退場，警隊剛離場後白衫暴徒再度進場，雙方異常合拍，彷如合舞。<br />\n<br />\n4.有大量被認出的721暴徒至今仍未被起訴，e.g. 恐怖分子陳志祥。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多，打唔哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e153a5541e25ce17f77b7141cf2d168caf12e1c5","tid":1659551,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:52:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"544daeeafa86df1d3e89d3cb8259c3c6eb616329","tid":1659551,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0635da0d3f14b2ce8429201c083405466bb66b17","tid":1659551,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T04:16:43.000Z","msg":"屌你老母張建宗<br />\n糾纏到你拉撚晒班仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T06:53:36.000Z","msg":"日日提<br />\n秒秒提<br />\n見到人打招呼都提"},{"pid":"0419cb731d0bf9bd149bd49c51a94ee97b1b4fcc","tid":1659551,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T07:08:40.000Z","msg":"831<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />新屋嶺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0001ac9bb89f3cbb1ffba34e18e5c5ac958bc0e5","tid":1659551,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T08:05:26.000Z","msg":"正苦新風向<br />\n分化唔到和勇就叫人忘記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過好似仲難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}